{html}<div><p>Any updates? Swipe still doesn't fire on views or windows with
1.5.1 or 1.6 CI.</p>
<pre>
<code>var swiped = 'none';
win.addEventListener('swipe', function(e){
    Ti.API.info('swiping '+e.direction+' by '+e.source);
    if (e.direction != swiped) {
        Ti.API.info('now we should be swiping '+e.direction);
        swiped = e.direction;
        if (e.direction == 'left') {
            //stuff
            nextTab();
        }
        else 
            if (e.direction == 'right') {
                //stuff
                previousTab();
            }
    }
    setTimeout(function() {
        swiped = 'none';
        },2000);
});</code>
</pre></div>{html}

{html}<div><p>Any word on when this will be fixed? Swiping is really important
on mobile. I'm using 1.5.1 and swiping is not working for a view,
webview, imageview, or scrollableview</p></div>{html}

